Package com.terracottatech.store.function

Interface BuildableToDoubleFunction<T>

All Superinterfaces:
ToDoubleFunction<T>
public interface BuildableToDoubleFunction<T> extends ToDoubleFunction<T>
A function of one argument that generates a double result, and supports building derived functional types.
